<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>New device login</title>
  </head>

  <body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#f5f6f7; font-family:Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;">
    <div style="max-width:640px; margin:48px auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:24px; padding:48px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);">
      <div style="text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.4em; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:#9ca3af; margin-bottom:24px;">
        define.
      </div>

      <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:32px; font-weight:800; color:#111827;">
        Login from a new device
      </h1>

      <p style="margin-top:16px; font-size:16px; color:#4b5563; line-height:1.65;">
        {{greeting}} we spotted a sign-in on your Define account that looks new. Review the details below—if
        everything looks familiar, no action is needed.
      </p>

      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top:24px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:24px; background-color:#f9fafb;">
        <tbody>
          {{#each rows}}
            <tr>
              <td style="width:35%; padding:12px 16px; font-size:11px; font-weight:600; color:#6b7280; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.08em;">
                {{this.label}}
              </td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px; font-size:14px; color:#111827;">
                {{this.value}}
              </td>
            </tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p style="margin-top:28px; font-size:14px; color:#6b7280;">
        Didn’t recognize this login? Reset your password right away and we’ll sign you out everywhere.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top:36px; font-size:14px; color:#9ca3af;">
        Need help? <a href="mailto:support@define.local" style="color:#111827;">Contact support</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
